Text: Kumarych, spasibo tebe, podday gazu, velikoye delo delaesh!
Kumarych, ty- Geniy, skachal!!! Spasibo tebe, zhdjom smirenno desyatoy chasti!!!
Da horosh, Berich, komplimentami sipat... Ja skromnyaga... ))) Poluchu posilochku s pervimi Sprutami skoro, zal'you... No poka ne mogu ranniie sezoni, jdite chervonca, on seichas pri mne...
